&lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; is a 1994 anglo-german drama film directed by iain softley . it chronicles the early days of the beatles in hamburg , germany . the film focuses primarily on the relationship between stuart sutcliffe ( stephen dorff ) and john lennon ( ian hart ) , and also with sutcliffe 's german girlfriend astrid &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; ( sheryl lee ) . it has subsequently been made into a stage production .